 Stefani]]\n|2017\n|<ref name=\"MoneyNation\">{{cite web|last1=Gerencer|first1=Tommy|title=How Much Money Do The Voice Coaches Make?|url=http://moneynation.com/how-much-money-do-the-voice-coaches-make/|website=MoneyNation|accessdate=July 4, 2017|date=November 28, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Nicki Minaj]]\n|''American Idol''\n|Judge\n|2012\u201313\n|<ref name=\"NickiIdol\">{{cite web|last1=Soghomonian|first1=Talia|title=Nicki Minaj and Mariah Carey quit \u2018American Idol\u2019|url=https://www.nme.com/news/tv/nicki-minaj-and-mariah-carey-quit-american-idol-881126|website=[[NME]]|accessdate=February 2, 2019|date=June 1, 2013}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Morning annual salaries==\n[[File:Ellen DeGeneres 2011.jpg|thumb|upright|120px|[[Ellen DeGeneres]], host of the eponymous [[The Ellen DeGeneres Show]]]]\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n|-  style=\"text-align:center; background:#d6d6d6;\"\n! Name\n! Program\n! Role\n! Salary\n! Year\n! {{abbr|Ref.|References}}\n|-\n|[[Ellen DeGeneres]]\n|''[[The Ellen DeGeneres Show]]''\n|[[Television presenter|Host]]\n|$77 million\n|2018\n| <ref>{{cite news | url=https://paywizard.org/salary/vip-check/talk-show-host-salaries | work=CBC News | title=TV Personalities | date=July 25, 2007 | access-date=September 7, 2018 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180908054254/https://paywizard.org/salary/vip-check/talk-show-host-salaries | archive-date=September 8, 2018 | url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Judith Sheindlin]]\n|''[[Judge Judy]]''\n|[[Judge]]\n|$47 million\n|2013\n| <ref>{{Cite news\n|title=TVs Highest Paid Star? Judge Judy (by a mile)\n|publisher=newser.com\n|url=http://www.newser.com/story/173000/tvs-highest-paid-star-judge-judy-by-a-mile.html\n|date= Aug 22, 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Barbara Walters]]\n|''[[The View (U.S. TV series)|The View]]''\n|[[Television presenter|Host]]\n|$13 million\n|2007\n|<ref>{{Cite news\n|url=https://www.forbes.com/lists/2007/53/07celebrities_Barbara-Walters_O4HQ.html\n|title=Barbara Walters\n|publisher=Forbes.com